            <p>How would you rate your level of knowledge or experience in the areas you selected?</p>

            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label><input type="radio" name="expertise" value="beginner" class="mr-2"> Beginner: Just started exploring the area</label><br>
                <label><input type="radio" name="expertise" value="intermediate" class="mr-2"> Intermediate: Have some experience or knowledge</label><br>
